data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of Taylor Ranch! This captivating residence boasts a must-see floor plan with an inviting open concept blending the living, kitchen, and dining areas. The kitchen offers ample countertop space and cabinets, creating an ideal environment for preparing and enjoying your favorite meals.Step into a tastefully updated space featuring 4 bedrooms with 1 and  3/4 baths. The primary bedroom is complete with a generous walk-in closet, offering a perfect blend of style and practicality.With a two-car garage, convenience is at your fingertips, providing parking and additional storage space. Beyond the boundaries of this charming abode lies a world of amenities, with shopping, entertainment, schools, and the enchanting Mariposa Basin Park.
